VALUES ('Jane Garden Freehold Townhomes', 'Markham', 'ON', 'York Regional Rd 7', 'High $700s', 'NOW SELLING', 'Primont Homes', 'When you''re purchasing a new home, you can benefit from all those years of experience. Primont Homes is committed to providing the highest quality and value to all our homebuyers. Prime locations, elegant design, superb craftsmanship and unrivaled customer service have made Primont a leading and trusted name in the industry. It''s been our privilege to build several dynamic, outstanding new communities of more than 3,000 homes in the GTA.', 'Homes', 'Fall 2021', '102 Units', '3-Storeys', 'Private Driveway', 'Freehold', '* Walking Distance to Cornell Community Centre * 3 Mins Drive to Markham Stouffville Hospital * 5 Mins Drive to Main St. Markham * 7 Mins Drive to Markham GO Station * Close to Shops, Restaurants & Schools * Many Nearby Public Transit Options * Rough Valley Park, Walker Park & Benjamin Marr Park is very close by', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_50_www.primonthomes.com-604407641563995.jpg', ARRAY['https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_51_www.primonthomes.com-604427850214586.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_50_www.primonthomes.com-604419745717259.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_50_www.primonthomes.com-604407641563995.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_49_www.primonthomes.com-604349516222089.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_49_www.primonthomes.com-604325916252750.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2019_03_01_05_31_49_1.jpg'], 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2977.1526511703473!2d-79.21955315536104!3d43.881938328565674!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89d4d7e5d57f0185%3A0xad5dbe8558c19392!2sCornell%20Rouge%20Blvd%