'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/TrendLiving-Building3-DigitalAd-600x600-3.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/TrendLiving-Building3-DigitalAd-600x600-2.jpg'], 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2901.6601205097936!2d-79.88406582428603!3d43.342300772484116!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x882c9d7d8ab177a3%3A0xde8fb051bf4bb55c!2sDundas%20St%20E%20%26%20Riverwalk%20Dr%2C%20Hamilton%2C%20ON%20L0R%202H7!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sca!4v1703632623022!5m2!1sen!2sca');

