VALUES ('M Condos', 'Brampton', 'ON', '2005 Wanless Drive', 'High $500S', 'NOW SELLING', 'Primont Homes', 'For 50 years, our company has followed the simple philosophy of building every home as if it''s our own, and treating every customer like they''re a member of the family. Now when you''re purchasing a new home, you can benefit from all those years of experience. Primont Homes is committed to providing the highest quality and value to all our homebuyers. Prime locations, elegant design, superb craftsmanship and unrivaled customer service have made Primont a leading and trusted name in the industry. It''s been our privilege to build several dynamic, outstanding new communities of more than 3,000 homes in the GTA.', 'Condos', 'May 2020', '75 Units', '8 Storeys', 'Included with Suites over 1,000 Sqft', '$0.49/sqft', 'Toronto Premium Outlets Bramalea City Centre Shopper''s World Brampton Starbucks A&W Longo''s Grocery Store Major Banks Brampton Bowling Centre Shoppers Drug Mart and much more.', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Primont-M-condo.jpg', ARRAY['https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Primont-M-condo.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Sitemap.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Gym-and-Fitness-Studio-at-M-Condos-10-v13-full-scaled.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Spa-Inspired-Bathrooms-at-M-Condos-12-v13-full-scaled.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/The-Elegant-Lobby-at-M-Condos-7-v13-full-scaled.jpg', 'https://builderbookings.ca/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/The-Sophisticated-Multi-purpose-room-at-M-Condos-8-v13-full-scaled.jpg'], 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2885.3544056607116!2d-79.84469724569401!3d43.6823949383918!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x882b139d60177f97%3A0x3d2ed2825b29b3fc!2sSandalwood%20Pkwy%20W%20%26%20Veterans%20Drive%2C%20Brampton%2C%20ON%20L7A%200B6!5e0!3m